data.lean: lemma mul_add (t a b : mynat) : t * (a + b) = t * a + t * b :=
data.editorText:
induction b with d hd,
rw add_zero a,
rw mul_zero t,
rw add_zero,
refl,
rw add_succ a d,
rw mul_succ t (a+d),
rw hd,
rw add_assoc (t*a) (t*d) t,
rw ← mul_succ t d,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_assoc (a b c : mynat) : (a * b) * c = a * (b * c) :=
data.editorText:
induction c with d hd,
rw mul_zero (a * b),
rw mul_zero b,
rw mul_zero a,
refl,
rw mul_succ (a*b) d,
rw hd,
rw ← mul_add a (b*d) b,
rw ← mul_succ b d,

data.lean: lemma succ_mul (a b : mynat) : succ a * b = a * b + b :=
data.editorText:
induction b with d hd,
rw mul_zero,
rw add_zero,
rw mul_zero,
refl,
rw succ_eq_add_one d,
rw mul_add (succ a) d 1,
rw hd,
rw ← succ_eq_add_one d,
rw mul_one (succ a),
rw add_assoc,
rw add_succ d a,
rw mul_succ a d,
rw add_assoc,
rw add_succ a d,
rw add_comm d a,
refl,

data.lean: lemma add_mul (a b t : mynat) : (a + b) * t = a * t + b * t :=
data.editorText:
induction t with d hd,
rw mul_zero (a+b), rw mul_zero a, rw mul_zero b,
rw add_zero 0,
refl,
rw mul_succ (a+b) d,
rw hd,
rw add_comm a b,
rw add_assoc (a*d) (b*d) (b+a),
rw ← add_assoc (b*d) b a,
rw ← mul_succ b d,
rw add_comm (a*d) (b * succ d + a),
rw add_assoc (b*succ d) a (a*d),
rw add_comm a (a*d),
rw ← mul_succ a d,
rw add_comm (b * succ d) (a * succ d),
refl,

data.lean: lemma zero_pow_succ (m : mynat) : (0 : mynat) ^ (succ m) = 0 :=
data.editorText:
rw pow_succ 0 m,
induction m with d hd,
rw zero_pow_zero,
rw mul_zero 1,
refl,
rw pow_succ 0 d,
rw hd,
rw mul_zero 0,
refl,

data.lean: lemma pow_add (a m n : mynat) : a ^ (m + n) = a ^ m * a ^ n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with d hd,
rw add_zero m,
rw pow_zero a,
rw mul_one (a ^ m),
refl,
rw add_succ m d,
rw pow_succ a (m+d),
rw hd,
rw mul_assoc (a^m) (a^d) a,
rw ← pow_succ a d,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_pow (a b n : mynat) : (a * b) ^ n = a ^ n * b ^ n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with d hd,
rw pow_zero (a*b),
rw pow_zero a,
rw pow_zero b,
rw one_mul 1,
refl,
rw pow_succ (a*b) d,
rw hd,
rw mul_assoc (a^d) (b^d) (a*b),
rw mul_comm a b,
rw ← mul_assoc (b^d) b a,
rw ← pow_succ b d,
rw mul_comm (b^succ d) a,
rw ← mul_assoc (a^d) a (b ^ succ d),
rw ← pow_succ a d,
refl,

data.lean: lemma pow_pow (a m n : mynat) : (a ^ m) ^ n = a ^ (m * n) :=
data.editorText:
induction n with d hd,
rw pow_zero (a^m),
rw mul_zero m,
rw pow_zero a,
refl,
rw pow_succ (a^m) d,
rw hd,
rw mul_succ m d,
rw pow_add a (m*d) m,
refl,

data.lean:
lemma add_squared (a b : mynat) :
  (a + b) ^ (2 : mynat) = a ^ (2 : mynat) + b ^ (2 : mynat) + 2 * a * b :=
data.editorText:
rw two_eq_succ_one,
  rw one_eq_succ_zero,
  repeat {rw pow_succ},
  rw pow_zero (a+b),
  rw pow_zero a,
  rw pow_zero b,
  rw one_mul (a+b),
  rw one_mul a,
  rw one_mul b,
  rw ← one_eq_succ_zero,
  rw succ_eq_add_one 1,
  rw mul_assoc (1+1) a b,
  rw add_mul 1 1 (a*b),
  rw one_mul (a*b),
  rw add_right_comm (a*a) (b*b) (a*b + a*b),
  rw ← add_assoc (a*a) (a*b) (a*b),
  rw ← mul_add a a b,
  rw add_assoc (a*(a+b)) (a*b) (b*b),
  rw ← add_mul a b b,
  rw mul_comm (a+b) b,
  rw ← add_mul a b (a+b),
  refl,

rw ← add_zero a at h,

data.lean: lemma ne_succ_self (n : mynat) : n ≠ succ n :=
data.editorText:
intro nsucc,
rw succ_eq_add_one n at nsucc,
rw ← add_zero n at nsucc,
rw add_assoc n 0 1 at nsucc,
rw zero_add 1 at nsucc,
have umzero := add_left_cancel n 0 1,
have boom := umzero nsucc,
rw one_eq_succ_zero at boom,
apply zero_ne_succ 0,
exact boom,
